./.relay/tickets/tkt_01krb21fnwxxpc73gt972jpetz.md:47:- Inspect the source handler behind `ticket:read` and `readTicketFile`; avoid relying on generated `out/main/index.js` as the edit target unless this project intentionally edits built output.
